OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe monarch is expected to tell US
OL,12,Flawmakers that the nations' "defence,
OL,13,Fintelligence and security ties are
OL,14,Fmeasured not in years but in decades"
OL,15,Fin a tacit acknowledgement of recent
OL,16,Fstrains between Trump and Prime
OL,17,FMinister Keir Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FCharles will also talk about his
OL,7,Ffaith, and express his belief that in
OL,8,Fthe hearts of the US and UK lies "a
OL,9,Fgenerosity of spirit and a duty to
OL,10,Ffoster compassion, to promote peace,
OL,11,Fto deepen mutual understanding and to
OL,12,Fvalue people of all faiths and none".
OL,14,FHe will note that the story of both
OL,15,Fnations over the last 250 years is one
OL,16,Fof "reconciliation and renewal",
OL,17,Fcalling it "one of the greatest
OL,18,Falliances in human history", which he
OL,19,Fhopes long into the future.
OL,26,@tD@dO]xD@DOUxD@_O]yD@LOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FCharles will also make a brief
OL,7,Freference to the shooting at a
OL,8,FWashington dinner attended by Trump on
OL,9,FSaturday night.
OL,11,FIt will be only the second time a
OL,12,FBritish monarch has addressed a joint
OL,13,Fmeeting of Congress in history, with
OL,14,FQueen Elizabeth becoming the first
OL,15,Fduring a state visit to the US in 1991.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FCharles' speech is expected to be a
OL,7,Fhighlight of the royal four-day visit
OL,8,Fto the US, which he and Queen Camilla
OL,9,Fkicked off on Monday by meeting Trump
OL,10,Fand his wife, Melania, at the White
OL,11,FHouse.
OL,13,FThe royal couple arrived at Joint Base
OL,14,FAndrews, near Washington DC, during
OL,15,Fthe afternoon, where they were greeted
OL,16,Fby US chief of protocol Monica Crowley
OL,17,Fand the British ambassador to the US,
OL,18,FSir Christian Turner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FThey were then driven in a motorcade
OL,7,Fto the White House, where they were
OL,8,Fmet by the president and first lady
OL,9,Fand shared tea in the Green Room,
OL,10,Fbefore being taken to see the state's
OL,11,Fnewly expanded beehive.
OL,13,FCharles and Camilla then went on to
OL,14,Fattend a traditional garden party at
OL,15,Fthe UK embassy, which was attended by
OL,16,FOlympic diver Tom Daley and Lioness
OL,17,Ffootballer Esme Morgan, along with
OL,18,FSenator Ted Cruz and the current
OL,19,Fspeaker of the house, Mike Johnson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FAs well as the joint Congress on
OL,7,FTuesday, Charles and Camilla will take
OL,8,Fpart in a State Arrival Ceremony
OL,9,Fhosted by the president and first lady
OL,10,Fon the South Lawn of the White House
OL,11,Fin the morning.
OL,13,FThis will mark the official arrival of
OL,14,Fthe royals, drawing upon a tradition
OL,15,Fthat dates back to the 18th century,
OL,16,Fwith a traditional military arrival
OL,17,Fceremony including honours by the US
OL,18,FArmy Herald Trumpets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FNational anthems of both countries
OL,7,Fwill be played by "The President's
OL,8,FOwn" US Marine Band, with the
OL,9,FPresidential Salute Battery rendering
OL,10,Fa 21-gun cannon salute.
OL,12,FFollowing an Inspection of the Troops
OL,13,Fand a Troop in Review, facilitated by
OL,14,Fthe US Army Fife and Drum Corps, the
OL,15,Fpresident will then deliver remarks
OL,16,Ffrom the South Lawn.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FAfterwards, both couples will proceed
OL,7,Fto the Blue Room Balcony, where they
OL,8,Fwill participate in a Pass in Review
OL,9,Fof 300 US Service Members and 500
OL,10,Fmembers of the US Armed Forces from
OL,11,Fall six military branches present at
OL,12,Fthe ceremony - a historic first for
OL,13,Fstate visits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777449958
OL,3,CKing to speak of 'reconciliation' in
OL,4,Chistoric Congress speech
OL,6,FThousands of guests will be gathered
OL,7,Fon the South Lawn, including Members
OL,8,Fof the President's Cabinet, Members of
OL,9,FCongress, the official Delegation of
OL,10,Fthe United States of America, the
OL,11,Fofficial Delegation of the UK,
OL,12,FAmerican military families and
OL,13,Fstudents from the British
OL,14,FInternational School of Washington.
OL,16,FThe King and Queen will then sign the
OL,17,FWhite House guest book and participate
OL,18,Fin an official gift exchange with the
OL,19,Fpresident and first lady in the Blue
OL,20,FRoom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
